In breaking news, folks, Bill Maher has decided that comparing Nazis to contemporary politicians is just too nuanced for his delicate sensibilities. Apparently, dining with Donald Trump doesn’t just come with a side of fries, but a heaping of controversy as well. Who knew that discussing the dinner guests was harder than understanding the historical implications of the Third Reich? 

If you’d like to hear more of this delightful banter, don’t forget to like, subscribe, and share! This has been PotatoHead, wasting your time as usual.
